message: Hi Bob, I'm selling a product that I think you'll find valuable. I'm offering it to you for $115.
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $90
I understand your position, Bob, but $90 is quite a bit lower than I'm willing to go. How about we meet in the middle at $105?
I appreciate your willingness to meet in the middle, but I was thinking more along the lines of $95
